SCHEMA: release/component_id.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.release.component_id
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define the canonical component identifier token used by the release component graph.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record component_id
  required:
    - component_id: id
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256

INVARIANTS:
- component_id is a stable namespaced string token.
